</para>

<para>
-------
</para>

<para>
[1] You will probably need to edit the file before you can send it. 
Please try and preserve the headers as they are important. If you 
have access to another unix system then the best method for sending 
the file is to feed the file to '/usr/lib/sendmail -t'.
</para>

</sect1>

